      <div class="msgContentFrame">I have been using this macro to some success as my &quot;Auto-Attack&quot; macro. <br /> <br />/ac &quot;Light Stab/Slash&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br />/ac &quot;Phalanx&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br />/ac &quot;Guard&quot; sub &lt;me&gt; <br /> <br />Does a pretty good job of catching Phalanx and raising my shield when it needs to be up. <br /> <br />Anyone else have any macros that attempt to automatically do Phalanx/Shield? <br /> <br />-Kash<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>I &quot;BAM!&quot; therefor I AM!</div></div>
