      <div class="msgContentFrame">try this <br /> <br /><pre>/ac &quot;Guard&quot; sub &lt;me&gt; 
/wait 3 
/ac &quot;Provoke&quot; &lt;t&gt; 
/wait 3 
/ac &quot;Phalanx&quot; &lt;t&gt; 
/wait 5 
/ac &quot;Phalanx&quot; &lt;t&gt;</pre> <br /> <br /> <br />You could lengthen this by adding another phalanx, or you could change the last one to like Light Stab then add another Phalanx. I have this macro and it works ok, but just triggering the skills manually works a lot better. You might need to adjust the wait times. <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1815754.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
